### Using ggformula

:::: {.columns}
:::{.column}

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
movies %>%
  drop_na() %>%
  gf_point(DomesticGross ~ WorldGross) %>%
  gf_lm() %>%
  gf_labs(
    title = "Scatter Plot",
    subtitle = "Movie Gross Earnings: Domestics vs World"
  )
